1
00:00:06,905 --> 00:00:10,705
<font color=#FFFF00>It said Hyung Seop drove your father to his death.</font>

2
00:00:15,875 --> 00:00:16,975
<font color=#FFFF00>That can't be true.</font>

3
00:00:17,845 --> 00:00:20,645
<font color=#FFFF00>- It can't be. My dad is... - Come to your senses.</font>

4
00:00:20,875 --> 00:00:23,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Your dad? Which one?</font>

5
00:00:23,845 --> 00:00:26,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you mean your current dad who lived in an expensive house...</font>

6
00:00:26,405 --> 00:00:29,475
<font color=#FFFF00>and acted superior because he worked at Seongsoo Trading Company?</font>

7
00:00:29,675 --> 00:00:33,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Or do you mean your real dad who got beaten up...</font>

8
00:00:33,305 --> 00:00:36,675
<font color=#FFFF00>and hung himself because he caused little injury...</font>

9
00:00:37,405 --> 00:00:38,575
<font color=#FFFF00>to rich folk's children?</font>

10
00:00:39,745 --> 00:00:41,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Which one are you talking about?</font>

11
00:00:42,345 --> 00:00:43,345
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe it.</font>

12
00:00:44,975 --> 00:00:46,175
<font color=#FFFF00>I just can't.</font>

13
00:00:49,245 --> 00:00:50,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Right.</font>

14
00:00:51,645 --> 00:00:54,905
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess it's natural that you find it hard to believe. Why?</font>

15
00:00:55,975 --> 00:01:00,145
<font color=#FFFF00>It's because Hyung Seop has been such a wonderful father to you.</font>

16
00:01:01,145 --> 00:01:02,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know that?</font>

17
00:01:03,045 --> 00:01:06,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Your father only cares about his children.</font>

18
00:01:08,545 --> 00:01:12,105
<font color=#FFFF00>Your sister Jeong Hwa was badly hurt, so he was furious.</font>

19
00:01:12,605 --> 00:01:16,075
<font color=#FFFF00>He was an arrogant person who would do anything for his children.</font>

20
00:01:16,905 --> 00:01:18,045
<font color=#FFFF00>After all that,</font>

21
00:01:18,675 --> 00:01:20,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Did he think raising that man's son as his own...</font>

22
00:01:21,005 --> 00:01:23,245
<font color=#FFFF00>was going to make up for what he's done?</font>

23
00:01:24,645 --> 00:01:28,945
<font color=#FFFF00>I might not be a wealthy and noble person,</font>

24
00:01:29,705 --> 00:01:32,975
<font color=#FFFF00>but I know others' children are also as precious as mine at least.</font>

25
00:01:45,845 --> 00:01:49,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, you shouldn't talk on the phone when you're driving.</font>

26
00:01:50,305 --> 00:01:51,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir,</font>

27
00:01:51,845 --> 00:01:54,475
<font color=#FFFF00>I was talking with my wife...</font>

28
00:01:54,545 --> 00:01:56,775
<font color=#FFFF00>because my kid got injured on his way to school this morning.</font>

29
00:01:56,775 --> 00:01:58,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Hang up already.</font>

30
00:01:58,675 --> 00:02:02,645
<font color=#FFFF00>You're in charge of kids' safety. You can't use your phone.</font>

31
00:02:03,175 --> 00:02:06,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir, he cares a lot about the kids.</font>

32
00:02:06,775 --> 00:02:08,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Please don't worry.</font>

33
00:02:08,405 --> 00:02:09,975
<font color=#FFFF00>How can I not be worried?</font>

34
00:02:10,005 --> 00:02:12,375
<font color=#FFFF00>How would I know if he usually talks on the phone...</font>

35
00:02:12,405 --> 00:02:14,275
<font color=#FFFF00>while he's driving or not?</font>

36
00:02:14,905 --> 00:02:18,345
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't do that. I told you my kid got hurt.</font>

37
00:02:18,445 --> 00:02:19,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey, let me call you later.</font>

38
00:02:20,345 --> 00:02:22,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Guys like you always cause car accidents...</font>

39
00:02:22,505 --> 00:02:25,575
<font color=#FFFF00>and get kids injured. Do you know that?</font>

40
00:02:25,575 --> 00:02:28,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir, can't you see that I hung up?</font>

41
00:02:28,115 --> 00:02:31,005
<font color=#FFFF00>- That's enough. - How dare you!</font>

42
00:02:31,745 --> 00:02:33,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandpa...</font>

43
00:02:34,045 --> 00:02:37,575
<font color=#FFFF00>He explained that his kid got hurt. Please give him a break.</font>

44
00:02:37,775 --> 00:02:40,905
<font color=#FFFF00>He even turned the engine off. Don't you think that's too much?</font>

45
00:02:41,745 --> 00:02:42,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Min Seok, get in.</font>

46
00:02:43,275 --> 00:02:45,345
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ah In, let's get in the car. - Forget it.</font>

47
00:02:45,775 --> 00:02:49,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't send her to the kindergarten today. Just leave by yourselves.</font>

48
00:02:50,475 --> 00:02:53,875
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll talk to the principal later.</font>

49
00:02:54,975 --> 00:02:57,705
<font color=#FFFF00>If you want to use your phone while you're driving,</font>

50
00:02:57,705 --> 00:03:00,375
<font color=#FFFF00>quit this job and find a new one. Okay?</font>

51
00:03:00,405 --> 00:03:03,245
<font color=#FFFF00>What will you tell the principal about me?</font>

52
00:03:03,405 --> 00:03:05,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir. Goodness.</font>

53
00:03:06,905 --> 00:03:08,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Seriously.</font>

54
00:03:20,845 --> 00:03:22,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Enough is enough.</font>

55
00:03:22,775 --> 00:03:24,305
<font color=#FFFF00>You're not the only one with grandchildren.</font>

56
00:03:26,545 --> 00:03:29,305
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with that old woman?</font>

57
00:03:29,375 --> 00:03:31,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandpa.</font>

58
00:03:33,645 --> 00:03:34,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah In.</font>

59
00:03:37,045 --> 00:03:41,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah In, let's have fun at home with me. Okay?</font>

60
00:03:41,405 --> 00:03:43,545
<font color=#FFFF00>No. I hate you.</font>

61
00:03:46,245 --> 00:03:47,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah In.</font>

62
00:03:48,375 --> 00:03:51,175
<font color=#FFFF00>It was for your safety.</font>

63
00:03:51,975 --> 00:03:54,105
<font color=#FFFF00>Would the driver be fired today?</font>

64
00:03:56,845 --> 00:03:57,875
<font color=#FFFF00>I have no idea.</font>

65
00:03:58,975 --> 00:04:01,605
<font color=#FFFF00>If he gets fired, hire him.</font>

66
00:04:02,105 --> 00:04:03,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry?</font>

67
00:04:04,245 --> 00:04:05,605
<font color=#FFFF00>He hasn't changed at all.</font>

68
00:04:06,545 --> 00:04:08,475
<font color=#FFFF00>He still cares about his children only.</font>

69
00:04:09,175 --> 00:04:11,505
<font color=#FFFF00>You know people don't change easily.</font>

70
00:04:24,915 --> 00:04:28,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Today, the executives of Golden Street will come...</font>

71
00:04:28,875 --> 00:04:30,575
<font color=#FFFF00>to Korea to see you.</font>

72
00:04:31,675 --> 00:04:33,175
<font color=#FFFF00>We could just have a video conference.</font>

73
00:04:33,875 --> 00:04:35,775
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess they wanted to come...</font>

74
00:04:36,045 --> 00:04:38,845
<font color=#FFFF00>and see how you're doing as your absence is prolonged.</font>

75
00:04:39,705 --> 00:04:41,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Right. I heard that Seong Joon hasn't come to work...</font>

76
00:04:41,875 --> 00:04:43,805
<font color=#FFFF00>since yesterday.</font>

77
00:04:44,175 --> 00:04:46,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Why is that? Does he no longer want to work?</font>

78
00:04:46,975 --> 00:04:50,175
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think so. It seems like he has some private problems.</font>

79
00:04:51,075 --> 00:04:52,675
<font color=#FFFF00>He didn't show up without notice.</font>

80
00:04:53,915 --> 00:04:54,945
<font color=#FFFF00>That is why...</font>

81
00:04:55,845 --> 00:04:59,275
<font color=#FFFF00>he didn't come to my place to beg me to let his girlfriend...</font>

82
00:04:59,345 --> 00:05:00,775
<font color=#FFFF00>keep writing the scenario.</font>

83
00:05:01,245 --> 00:05:03,975
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you plan to do with Jeong Hwa?</font>

84
00:05:07,745 --> 00:05:08,915
<font color=#FFFF00>As you can easily expect,</font>

85
00:05:09,975 --> 00:05:11,415
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll have dinners...</font>

86
00:05:12,415 --> 00:05:13,945
<font color=#FFFF00>and watch movies with her.</font>

87
00:05:20,675 --> 00:05:22,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

88
00:05:22,705 --> 00:05:25,205
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ah In, stop running. - Ah In.</font>

89
00:05:25,975 --> 00:05:27,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you back home?</font>

90
00:05:27,705 --> 00:05:29,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandpa told me not to go to the kindergarten.</font>

91
00:05:30,905 --> 00:05:32,345
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you...</font>

92
00:05:32,705 --> 00:05:36,445
<font color=#FFFF00>The driver kept talking on the phone while he was driving.</font>

93
00:05:36,575 --> 00:05:39,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll talk to the principal first. Send her tomorrow.</font>

94
00:05:39,905 --> 00:05:43,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Father, the driver is a really nice person.</font>

95
00:05:43,545 --> 00:05:46,105
<font color=#FFFF00>It doesn't matter if he's nice or not.</font>

96
00:05:46,105 --> 00:05:48,675
<font color=#FFFF00>He shouldn't be talking on the phone in the bus.</font>

97
00:05:48,805 --> 00:05:51,705
<font color=#FFFF00>It might turn into a habit, and who knows what will happen?</font>

98
00:05:52,545 --> 00:05:53,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Father.</font>

99
00:05:54,045 --> 00:05:56,575
<font color=#FFFF00>I have to go to work today.</font>

100
00:05:56,645 --> 00:05:58,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry. I will watch Ah In today.</font>

101
00:05:59,245 --> 00:06:00,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Really?</font>

102
00:06:00,675 --> 00:06:02,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I will watch her when I watch Ye Bin.</font>

103
00:06:03,345 --> 00:06:04,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Where's your mother-in-law?</font>

104
00:06:04,705 --> 00:06:07,405
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think she can get up today.</font>

105
00:06:07,405 --> 00:06:09,145
<font color=#FFFF00>That's understandable.</font>

106
00:06:09,775 --> 00:06:10,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother.</font>

107
00:06:12,445 --> 00:06:15,275
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't like you. You should get out.</font>

108
00:06:15,545 --> 00:06:17,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I will talk Jeong Hwa out of it.</font>

109
00:06:17,975 --> 00:06:19,975
<font color=#FFFF00>What will you tell her? What?</font>

110
00:06:20,305 --> 00:06:22,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think she will listen to you just because you talk to her?</font>

111
00:06:24,345 --> 00:06:26,675
<font color=#FFFF00>- But still... - I don't know.</font>

112
00:06:26,845 --> 00:06:27,905
<font color=#FFFF00>I have no idea.</font>

113
00:06:28,405 --> 00:06:31,405
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't even want to look at you. Get out.</font>

114
00:06:52,505 --> 00:06:55,075
<font color=#FFFF00>He still hasn't called me.</font>

115
00:06:56,375 --> 00:06:58,145
<font color=#FFFF00>How inconsiderate.</font>

116
00:07:02,005 --> 00:07:03,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it because of Jeong Hwa?</font>

117
00:07:09,775 --> 00:07:11,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh. Are you there?</font>

118
00:07:12,205 --> 00:07:13,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Come in.</font>

119
00:07:14,745 --> 00:07:15,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

120
00:07:17,145 --> 00:07:18,675
<font color=#FFFF00>It's before you head out for work, right?</font>

121
00:07:19,445 --> 00:07:20,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry to bother you in the morning.</font>

122
00:07:21,145 --> 00:07:22,275
<font color=#FFFF00>You are not bothering me.</font>

123
00:07:22,675 --> 00:07:26,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon didn't come home last night.</font>

124
00:07:26,345 --> 00:07:29,175
<font color=#FFFF00>I was wondering if something happened at work.</font>

125
00:07:30,505 --> 00:07:32,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

126
00:07:32,405 --> 00:07:35,945
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard he went to the countryside for an urgent matter.</font>

127
00:07:36,205 --> 00:07:38,145
<font color=#FFFF00>To the countryside? Why?</font>

128
00:07:38,775 --> 00:07:41,505
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know. I only heard it through a phone call.</font>

129
00:07:41,775 --> 00:07:42,905
<font color=#FFFF00>What a brat.</font>

130
00:07:43,045 --> 00:07:46,275
<font color=#FFFF00>He should have called me to let me know.</font>

131
00:07:46,475 --> 00:07:48,005
<font color=#FFFF00>How can he do this?</font>

132
00:07:49,975 --> 00:07:52,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, I am relieved to hear...</font>

133
00:07:52,205 --> 00:07:53,905
<font color=#FFFF00>he contacted you.</font>

134
00:07:54,845 --> 00:07:56,345
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry to barge in at this hour.</font>

135
00:07:56,775 --> 00:07:58,305
<font color=#FFFF00>You should get ready for work.</font>

136
00:07:58,705 --> 00:07:59,875
<font color=#FFFF00>I will.</font>

137
00:08:07,145 --> 00:08:09,275
<font color=#FFFF00>The number you have dialed is unavailable.</font>

138
00:08:09,375 --> 00:08:10,445
<font color=#FFFF00>- You'll be connected... - It's...</font>

139
00:08:10,445 --> 00:08:11,475
<font color=#FFFF00>- to voicemail. - turned off.</font>

140
00:08:12,175 --> 00:08:13,305
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on?</font>

141
00:08:19,575 --> 00:08:22,175
<font color=#FFFF00>What is wrong with you? What have I done wrong?</font>

142
00:08:22,845 --> 00:08:24,545
<font color=#FFFF00>You really don't know what you've done?</font>

143
00:08:24,545 --> 00:08:25,975
<font color=#FFFF00>What? What have I done?</font>

144
00:08:25,975 --> 00:08:27,975
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you throw a tantrum after you drank?</font>

145
00:08:28,045 --> 00:08:29,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that the way to behave in front of our parents?</font>

146
00:08:29,545 --> 00:08:31,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey, honey!</font>

147
00:08:31,275 --> 00:08:34,105
<font color=#FFFF00>- Let go of me. - What have you done right?</font>

148
00:08:34,275 --> 00:08:36,105
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - I heard...</font>

149
00:08:36,275 --> 00:08:38,675
<font color=#FFFF00>you made our parents worry the most.</font>

150
00:08:38,875 --> 00:08:41,245
<font color=#FFFF00>You got laid off and was hurt at a construction site.</font>

151
00:08:41,375 --> 00:08:44,075
<font color=#FFFF00>You opened that restaurant with our parents' pension, right?</font>

152
00:08:44,075 --> 00:08:46,015
<font color=#FFFF00>- You little brat. - Jeong Hwa.</font>

153
00:08:46,015 --> 00:08:47,945
<font color=#FFFF00>You moved in here, but I can't?</font>

154
00:08:48,015 --> 00:08:50,015
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't stay at my parent's house comfortably?</font>

155
00:08:50,205 --> 00:08:52,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I lived with my mother-in-law for seven years.</font>

156
00:08:52,945 --> 00:08:55,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Why can't I make myself at home in this house?</font>

157
00:08:55,275 --> 00:08:57,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, this isn't your house. This is dad's and mom's house.</font>

158
00:08:57,775 --> 00:08:59,345
<font color=#FFFF00>You are living off them too!</font>

159
00:08:59,545 --> 00:09:02,805
<font color=#FFFF00>You aren't the only one. Seong Sik is also living off them.</font>

160
00:09:02,805 --> 00:09:04,475
<font color=#FFFF00>So why are you picking on me?</font>

161
00:09:06,015 --> 00:09:08,305
<font color=#FFFF00>What on earth are you doing?</font>

162
00:09:08,945 --> 00:09:10,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you yelling?</font>

163
00:09:11,205 --> 00:09:13,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you want your mother to hear this too?</font>

164
00:09:14,745 --> 00:09:16,345
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dad. - Father.</font>

165
00:09:17,045 --> 00:09:18,375
<font color=#FFFF00>You brats.</font>

166
00:09:19,175 --> 00:09:20,905
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry, Dad.</font>

167
00:09:21,745 --> 00:09:22,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo.</font>

168
00:09:23,305 --> 00:09:24,545
<font color=#FFFF00>You should go to work.</font>

169
00:09:24,905 --> 00:09:27,345
<font color=#FFFF00>- Seong Hoon. Let's talk. - Okay.</font>

170
00:09:27,515 --> 00:09:29,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa. You should get up now.</font>

171
00:09:40,375 --> 00:09:41,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa.</font>

172
00:09:41,945 --> 00:09:43,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Enough is enough.</font>

173
00:09:43,345 --> 00:09:44,775
<font color=#FFFF00>What's the matter with you?</font>

174
00:09:48,205 --> 00:09:49,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Nowadays,</font>

175
00:09:49,575 --> 00:09:52,305
<font color=#FFFF00>divorce isn't considered to be a flaw,</font>

176
00:09:52,515 --> 00:09:54,305
<font color=#FFFF00>but it's not something to be proud of.</font>

177
00:09:54,375 --> 00:09:56,375
<font color=#FFFF00>No matter how difficult it is,</font>

178
00:09:56,605 --> 00:10:00,145
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think taking it out on your family is right.</font>

179
00:10:00,145 --> 00:10:01,545
<font color=#FFFF00>It's because I am stressed out.</font>

180
00:10:02,705 --> 00:10:04,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you the only one who's stressed?</font>

181
00:10:04,545 --> 00:10:06,675
<font color=#FFFF00>We are even more stressed out because of you.</font>

182
00:10:06,675 --> 00:10:09,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Say that your stress level is 10, then our level is 100.</font>

183
00:10:10,075 --> 00:10:11,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Besides, you know what?</font>

184
00:10:11,805 --> 00:10:15,305
<font color=#FFFF00>The road you walked on before you got married was destroyed.</font>

185
00:10:15,545 --> 00:10:17,275
<font color=#FFFF00>- What did you say? - That's why...</font>

186
00:10:17,275 --> 00:10:18,575
<font color=#FFFF00>your nickname is radioactivity.</font>

187
00:10:18,675 --> 00:10:19,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo.</font>

188
00:10:19,875 --> 00:10:21,875
<font color=#FFFF00>It's been 17 years since I've been married.</font>

189
00:10:21,905 --> 00:10:23,805
<font color=#FFFF00>You can treat me like a sister.</font>

190
00:10:23,905 --> 00:10:27,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Look who's talking. You brought your grandmother and cousin.</font>

191
00:10:27,545 --> 00:10:28,575
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

192
00:10:29,275 --> 00:10:30,545
<font color=#FFFF00>"Look who's talking"?</font>

193
00:10:31,045 --> 00:10:32,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you start a fight with her?</font>

194
00:10:33,575 --> 00:10:36,575
<font color=#FFFF00>She has enough on her plate. She's already stressed out.</font>

195
00:10:37,605 --> 00:10:39,345
<font color=#FFFF00>She was so rude...</font>

196
00:10:39,575 --> 00:10:41,305
<font color=#FFFF00>in front of you and Mom.</font>

197
00:10:41,575 --> 00:10:42,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Leave her alone.</font>

198
00:10:43,345 --> 00:10:46,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Ye Bin will treat her the same way when she gets old.</font>

199
00:10:47,775 --> 00:10:48,905
<font color=#FFFF00>You must be upset.</font>

200
00:10:49,805 --> 00:10:52,975
<font color=#FFFF00>As your mother said, I don't know what children mean to me.</font>

201
00:10:54,545 --> 00:10:55,675
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

202
00:10:55,875 --> 00:10:57,605
<font color=#FFFF00>I shouldn't have burdened you.</font>

203
00:10:58,105 --> 00:10:59,245
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

204
00:11:00,475 --> 00:11:02,405
<font color=#FFFF00>I am not doing so well.</font>

205
00:11:03,445 --> 00:11:05,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Running a fried chicken restaurant is good enough.</font>

206
00:11:06,245 --> 00:11:07,305
<font color=#FFFF00>How about Seong Sik?</font>

207
00:11:08,205 --> 00:11:11,575
<font color=#FFFF00>He always makes mistakes and is very clumsy.</font>

208
00:11:11,605 --> 00:11:12,675
<font color=#FFFF00>That's how he is.</font>

209
00:11:13,545 --> 00:11:15,745
<font color=#FFFF00>What other choice do you have? You are his brother.</font>

210
00:11:16,145 --> 00:11:17,945
<font color=#FFFF00>You should take care of him.</font>

211
00:11:22,405 --> 00:11:24,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Which brings me to my next point.</font>

212
00:11:28,805 --> 00:11:31,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Why would you want to run another business?</font>

213
00:11:31,145 --> 00:11:33,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad. This time, it will certainly make profits.</font>

214
00:11:33,545 --> 00:11:35,605
<font color=#FFFF00>- Seong Hoon. - I can't...</font>

215
00:11:35,605 --> 00:11:37,605
<font color=#FFFF00>live off you forever.</font>

216
00:11:37,605 --> 00:11:40,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa came back, and Seong Sik is struggling too.</font>

217
00:11:40,545 --> 00:11:43,545
<font color=#FFFF00>I should lead our family since I am the oldest son.</font>

218
00:11:44,105 --> 00:11:45,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Before I do that,</font>

219
00:11:45,845 --> 00:11:48,975
<font color=#FFFF00>I should move out so that you won't be stressed out about me.</font>

220
00:11:49,205 --> 00:11:52,075
<font color=#FFFF00>I can also save my face in front of my younger siblings. Dad.</font>

221
00:11:53,045 --> 00:11:54,575
<font color=#FFFF00>The money that goes into my children...</font>

222
00:11:54,875 --> 00:11:56,745
<font color=#FFFF00>isn't a small amount.</font>

223
00:11:57,875 --> 00:12:01,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if it isn't, how could you think this way?</font>

224
00:12:01,445 --> 00:12:03,745
<font color=#FFFF00>The item for this business will be successful for certain.</font>

225
00:12:04,075 --> 00:12:07,005
<font color=#FFFF00>I've been thinking for a long time since my days as a journalist.</font>

226
00:12:07,005 --> 00:12:08,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, right.</font>

227
00:12:08,905 --> 00:12:11,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee, the neighbor decided to help me as well.</font>

228
00:12:13,105 --> 00:12:14,505
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mr. Lee? - Yes.</font>

229
00:12:14,505 --> 00:12:16,405
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mr. Lee across the street? - Yes.</font>

230
00:12:16,545 --> 00:12:20,375
<font color=#FFFF00>What kind of a person is he?</font>

231
00:12:20,405 --> 00:12:22,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Lately, he is low in my favor.</font>

232
00:12:23,175 --> 00:12:25,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad. He had his reasons.</font>

233
00:12:25,505 --> 00:12:27,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you certain Mr. Lee will help you?</font>

234
00:12:27,905 --> 00:12:28,905
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm certain.</font>

235
00:12:29,275 --> 00:12:31,175
<font color=#FFFF00>So I ask you that you help me...</font>

236
00:12:31,245 --> 00:12:32,805
<font color=#FFFF00>just this once.</font>

237
00:12:33,245 --> 00:12:36,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you keep this a secret from Hye Joo for now?</font>

238
00:12:37,805 --> 00:12:40,945
<font color=#FFFF00>- But still... - Dad.</font>

239
00:12:41,245 --> 00:12:42,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

240
00:12:44,345 --> 00:12:45,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. Mr. Lee.</font>

241
00:12:46,875 --> 00:12:48,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you talk now?</font>

242
00:12:48,605 --> 00:12:50,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I can.</font>

243
00:12:50,605 --> 00:12:52,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are you now?</font>

244
00:12:52,605 --> 00:12:54,075
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm at a company I invested in.</font>

245
00:12:54,675 --> 00:12:57,345
<font color=#FFFF00>I invested my money. I ought to follow through to see how it is.</font>

246
00:12:57,475 --> 00:12:59,245
<font color=#FFFF00>This is my life.</font>

247
00:13:00,605 --> 00:13:02,445
<font color=#FFFF00>As is your right, of course.</font>

248
00:13:03,505 --> 00:13:04,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

249
00:13:05,305 --> 00:13:06,605
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way,</font>

250
00:13:06,675 --> 00:13:09,675
<font color=#FFFF00>I'd like to meet you regarding the business we've discussed before.</font>

251
00:13:10,175 --> 00:13:12,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Will you be available in the afternoon?</font>

252
00:13:12,505 --> 00:13:14,675
<font color=#FFFF00>I am. Let's meet then.</font>

253
00:13:15,075 --> 00:13:16,545
<font color=#FFFF00>I will contact you later.</font>

254
00:13:17,075 --> 00:13:19,675
<font color=#FFFF00>All right. Thank you. I will see you later.</font>

255
00:13:22,575 --> 00:13:25,045
<font color=#FFFF00>It's either go big or go home.</font>

256
00:13:25,645 --> 00:13:26,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Life is hard.</font>

257
00:13:31,105 --> 00:13:33,445
<font color=#FFFF00>It's cold. This is heavy.</font>

258
00:13:34,605 --> 00:13:37,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon! How can you come to work so late?</font>

259
00:13:37,505 --> 00:13:38,875
<font color=#FFFF00>So what if you are the owner?</font>

260
00:13:39,375 --> 00:13:40,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Carry these now.</font>

261
00:13:40,905 --> 00:13:42,775
<font color=#FFFF00>The headquarter sent us chickens.</font>

262
00:13:43,045 --> 00:13:45,305
<font color=#FFFF00>You are so loud this morning.</font>

263
00:13:45,305 --> 00:13:47,875
<font color=#FFFF00>It's because you don't do anything since you are the owner.</font>

264
00:13:47,875 --> 00:13:49,805
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean I don't do anything?</font>

265
00:13:49,805 --> 00:13:52,045
<font color=#FFFF00>You never do anything. Just now, you were on the phone, not helping me.</font>

266
00:13:53,575 --> 00:13:56,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Who was it on the phone? Whom were you talking to?</font>

267
00:13:56,445 --> 00:13:57,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't be so nosy.</font>

268
00:13:58,245 --> 00:14:01,105
<font color=#FFFF00>There's no law that says I must work with someone like you all day long.</font>

269
00:14:01,175 --> 00:14:03,245
<font color=#FFFF00>- Take this. - This isn't even heavy.</font>

270
00:14:03,245 --> 00:14:04,575
<font color=#FFFF00>- You jerk. - Do you think I want...</font>

271
00:14:04,575 --> 00:14:06,345
<font color=#FFFF00>to spend an entire day with you?</font>

272
00:14:06,745 --> 00:14:07,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't kid yourself.</font>

273
00:14:08,975 --> 00:14:10,975
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm so mad. I'm so annoyed.</font>

274
00:14:11,375 --> 00:14:12,675
<font color=#FFFF00>President Lee.</font>

275
00:14:14,445 --> 00:14:16,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry to have kept you waiting.</font>

276
00:14:16,605 --> 00:14:17,605
<font color=#FFFF00>There's no need.</font>

277
00:14:18,475 --> 00:14:19,975
<font color=#FFFF00>- Please take a seat. - Sure.</font>

278
00:14:21,805 --> 00:14:24,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang is testing...</font>

279
00:14:24,745 --> 00:14:27,475
<font color=#FFFF00>our new products. So here I am.</font>

280
00:14:27,975 --> 00:14:31,675
<font color=#FFFF00>I have something to discuss with you.</font>

281
00:14:32,445 --> 00:14:34,145
<font color=#FFFF00>You do?</font>

282
00:14:34,675 --> 00:14:35,875
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it regarding?</font>

283
00:14:38,845 --> 00:14:41,205
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm thinking of withdrawing my investment...</font>

284
00:14:41,245 --> 00:14:43,105
<font color=#FFFF00>if the project continues to go on as it is now.</font>

285
00:14:45,545 --> 00:14:47,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do you say that?</font>

286
00:14:49,145 --> 00:14:51,845
<font color=#FFFF00>The way Director Han works is very different...</font>

287
00:14:51,845 --> 00:14:52,905
<font color=#FFFF00>from my approach of handling business.</font>

288
00:14:53,805 --> 00:14:56,445
<font color=#FFFF00>It seems he doesn't think about money at all.</font>

289
00:14:56,845 --> 00:14:59,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Doing whatever he wants to do isn't exactly called running a business.</font>

290
00:15:00,675 --> 00:15:01,675
<font color=#FFFF00>On top of that,</font>

291
00:15:02,405 --> 00:15:05,345
<font color=#FFFF00>the rate the project is developing is quite slow.</font>

292
00:15:06,745 --> 00:15:09,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I came to meet with Director Han and Bang regarding this matter,</font>

293
00:15:10,045 --> 00:15:12,145
<font color=#FFFF00>but I couldn't even meet with them.</font>

294
00:15:12,345 --> 00:15:14,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang is in charge of...</font>

295
00:15:15,275 --> 00:15:18,005
<font color=#FFFF00>supervising FGC's overall business.</font>

296
00:15:18,005 --> 00:15:19,375
<font color=#FFFF00>What about Director Han?</font>

297
00:15:21,705 --> 00:15:25,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Well... Director Han is...</font>

298
00:15:26,875 --> 00:15:29,675
<font color=#FFFF00>From my perspective, I've invested a large sum of money.</font>

299
00:15:30,045 --> 00:15:32,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think I'll be in a pickle if this continues?</font>

300
00:15:33,345 --> 00:15:36,275
<font color=#FFFF00>The company might think that producing a drama is an excuse...</font>

301
00:15:36,275 --> 00:15:37,605
<font color=#FFFF00>and I went to Korea to have fun and waste my investment.</font>

302
00:15:38,145 --> 00:15:41,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Which made me think that it's not a bad idea...</font>

303
00:15:41,875 --> 00:15:43,975
<font color=#FFFF00>for me to stop here.</font>

304
00:15:49,605 --> 00:15:51,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you not approve of...</font>

305
00:15:52,305 --> 00:15:55,045
<font color=#FFFF00>- Director Han? - Well...</font>

306
00:15:56,445 --> 00:16:00,105
<font color=#FFFF00>I decided to make an invest because of him in the beginning.</font>

307
00:16:01,745 --> 00:16:05,405
<font color=#FFFF00>But as we proceeded with it, I couldn't trust him anymore.</font>

308
00:16:07,575 --> 00:16:10,775
<font color=#FFFF00>If the project goes wrong, I'm the one who'd suffer a loss.</font>

309
00:16:11,905 --> 00:16:14,445
<font color=#FFFF00>You wouldn't be the only one who'd suffer a loss...</font>

310
00:16:15,045 --> 00:16:17,045
<font color=#FFFF00>if things go wrong.</font>

311
00:16:20,375 --> 00:16:23,905
<font color=#FFFF00>There must be someone who'll be held accountable for this project.</font>

312
00:16:25,675 --> 00:16:27,575
<font color=#FFFF00>That is...</font>

313
00:16:29,075 --> 00:16:30,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that Director Han?</font>

314
00:16:36,575 --> 00:16:39,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course. Our company can lay...</font>

315
00:16:40,305 --> 00:16:43,545
<font color=#FFFF00>all the legal and financial responsibilities...</font>

316
00:16:43,645 --> 00:16:46,045
<font color=#FFFF00>on Director Han.</font>

317
00:16:46,045 --> 00:16:50,905
<font color=#FFFF00>That is why he is working really hard.</font>

318
00:16:51,005 --> 00:16:53,005
<font color=#FFFF00>His life can be at stake.</font>

319
00:16:55,245 --> 00:16:58,245
<font color=#FFFF00>- Is that so? - Sure.</font>

320
00:17:00,305 --> 00:17:03,275
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm relieved to hear that.</font>

321
00:17:08,245 --> 00:17:10,775
<font color=#FFFF00>The number you have dialed is unavailable...</font>

322
00:17:27,305 --> 00:17:29,475
<font color=#FFFF00>How is writing the scenario going these days?</font>

323
00:17:29,975 --> 00:17:31,805
<font color=#FFFF00>It's good. I'm doing my best.</font>

324
00:17:35,145 --> 00:17:38,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know that I made an investment in that drama?</font>

325
00:17:40,275 --> 00:17:41,275
<font color=#FFFF00>I do.</font>

326
00:17:42,375 --> 00:17:43,445
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

327
00:17:45,445 --> 00:17:47,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Speaking of it,</font>

328
00:17:48,715 --> 00:17:52,675
<font color=#FFFF00>could you please leave Director Han alone?</font>

329
00:17:53,945 --> 00:17:55,245
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean by that?</font>

330
00:17:57,275 --> 00:18:00,215
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll try my best with the scenario...</font>

331
00:18:00,345 --> 00:18:02,775
<font color=#FFFF00>until you're satisfied with it.</font>

332
00:18:04,845 --> 00:18:08,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you please stop meddling with the project...</font>

333
00:18:09,845 --> 00:18:12,275
<font color=#FFFF00>so that he can make the best of his capabilities?</font>

334
00:18:15,675 --> 00:18:19,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you backbite me in your room on the rooftop?</font>

335
00:18:19,805 --> 00:18:21,875
<font color=#FFFF00>No, we don't.</font>

336
00:18:21,905 --> 00:18:24,345
<font color=#FFFF00>He's not that kind of person.</font>

337
00:18:24,345 --> 00:18:26,175
<font color=#FFFF00>He'd never do that.</font>

338
00:18:27,945 --> 00:18:30,845
<font color=#FFFF00>- Why do you cover up for him? - Sorry?</font>

339
00:18:31,445 --> 00:18:33,975
<font color=#FFFF00>I almost thought you're his girlfriend.</font>

340
00:18:39,745 --> 00:18:42,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, I appreciate your opinion.</font>

341
00:18:43,745 --> 00:18:46,745
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll take that into account. See you.</font>

342
00:18:48,045 --> 00:18:51,715
<font color=#FFFF00>I promise to do my best.</font>

343
00:18:51,975 --> 00:18:55,045
<font color=#FFFF00>We can do it. Thank you in advance.</font>

344
00:19:09,345 --> 00:19:12,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir, what are you doing here?</font>

345
00:19:16,575 --> 00:19:17,775
<font color=#FFFF00>It's very sunny today.</font>

346
00:19:19,405 --> 00:19:20,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Spring is here.</font>

347
00:19:21,645 --> 00:19:23,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Did something happen?</font>

348
00:19:25,505 --> 00:19:27,075
<font color=#FFFF00>No, nothing happened.</font>

349
00:19:28,745 --> 00:19:30,345
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm just enjoying the lovely weather.</font>

350
00:19:31,545 --> 00:19:32,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

351
00:19:35,905 --> 00:19:38,405
<font color=#FFFF00>I have no idea what I am doing now.</font>

352
00:19:39,405 --> 00:19:41,045
<font color=#FFFF00>You're taking revenge.</font>

353
00:19:44,275 --> 00:19:46,345
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you have to put it that way?</font>

354
00:19:55,005 --> 00:19:57,105
<font color=#FFFF00>I met Dong Hui who lives on the rooftop room.</font>

355
00:19:59,175 --> 00:20:01,605
<font color=#FFFF00>I could see that she really likes Seong Joon.</font>

356
00:20:02,405 --> 00:20:03,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you jealous?</font>

357
00:20:05,675 --> 00:20:06,715
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

358
00:20:08,405 --> 00:20:09,645
<font color=#FFFF00>It was disgusting instead.</font>

359
00:20:14,675 --> 00:20:15,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Well,</font>

360
00:20:16,475 --> 00:20:18,045
<font color=#FFFF00>I was a little jealous too.</font>

361
00:20:19,405 --> 00:20:22,375
<font color=#FFFF00>I was thinking what I did in her age.</font>

362
00:20:24,605 --> 00:20:27,715
<font color=#FFFF00>All I did were studying and working all day long.</font>

363
00:20:29,405 --> 00:20:30,675
<font color=#FFFF00>As you said,</font>

364
00:20:31,845 --> 00:20:34,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I spent my young days planning the revenge...</font>

365
00:20:36,345 --> 00:20:38,345
<font color=#FFFF00>and looking for my brother.</font>

366
00:20:39,505 --> 00:20:42,745
<font color=#FFFF00>And he has a family who cares about him so much...</font>

367
00:20:43,445 --> 00:20:45,805
<font color=#FFFF00>and a girlfriend who loves him.</font>

368
00:20:47,145 --> 00:20:48,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir.</font>

369
00:20:49,875 --> 00:20:51,945
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not too late to back out.</font>

370
00:20:55,715 --> 00:20:58,215
<font color=#FFFF00>You know how wicked I am.</font>

371
00:21:00,305 --> 00:21:01,345
<font color=#FFFF00>What's with you?</font>

372
00:21:07,775 --> 00:21:08,875
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way,</font>

373
00:21:09,715 --> 00:21:11,645
<font color=#FFFF00>is your uncle's family all right?</font>

374
00:21:13,075 --> 00:21:14,075
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure...</font>

375
00:21:14,805 --> 00:21:17,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee would never let his family live happily.</font>

376
00:21:31,675 --> 00:21:34,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook, what brings you here?</font>

377
00:21:35,215 --> 00:21:36,215
<font color=#FFFF00>Is Aunt here?</font>

378
00:21:36,645 --> 00:21:39,475
<font color=#FFFF00>- She's in her room. - I see.</font>

379
00:21:39,845 --> 00:21:41,375
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you come to my house?</font>

380
00:21:43,215 --> 00:21:44,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Aunt.</font>

381
00:21:45,175 --> 00:21:48,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Then, I'm leaving.</font>

382
00:21:48,545 --> 00:21:49,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you trying to run away?</font>

383
00:21:50,345 --> 00:21:52,475
<font color=#FFFF00>This is all your fault.</font>

384
00:21:52,805 --> 00:21:56,975
<font color=#FFFF00>You met him when you were on a trip and made him return to Korea.</font>

385
00:21:57,175 --> 00:22:00,305
<font color=#FFFF00>This time, Hee Sook dragged him into my mom's house.</font>

386
00:22:00,675 --> 00:22:03,305
<font color=#FFFF00>What on earth do you think you're doing now?</font>

387
00:22:03,675 --> 00:22:05,875
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean Hee Sook dragged him in?</font>

388
00:22:06,975 --> 00:22:09,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, Jeong Eun,</font>

389
00:22:09,905 --> 00:22:11,405
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll explain to you later.</font>

390
00:22:11,675 --> 00:22:14,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry and leave. You should go.</font>

391
00:22:14,375 --> 00:22:17,075
<font color=#FFFF00>You're always the worst troublemaker.</font>

392
00:22:17,745 --> 00:22:20,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Eun, please leave. I'll see you later.</font>

393
00:22:27,875 --> 00:22:30,045
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aunt. - Shut it.</font>

394
00:22:30,405 --> 00:22:33,975
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you want me to do? Chang Soo has no instructor...</font>

395
00:22:34,105 --> 00:22:35,905
<font color=#FFFF00>to help him to prepare for the coming competition.</font>

396
00:22:36,405 --> 00:22:38,105
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean he has no instructor?</font>

397
00:22:38,605 --> 00:22:41,045
<font color=#FFFF00>There are many instructors out there.</font>

398
00:22:41,105 --> 00:22:43,045
<font color=#FFFF00>But he needs a world-class instructor.</font>

399
00:22:43,205 --> 00:22:45,705
<font color=#FFFF00>So did you have to open up my old wound...</font>

400
00:22:45,805 --> 00:22:48,205
<font color=#FFFF00>just to find a good teacher for Chang Soo?</font>

401
00:22:48,675 --> 00:22:50,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you say it's a wound?</font>

402
00:22:50,505 --> 00:22:53,005
<font color=#FFFF00>- Don't you think it's so romantic? - What?</font>

403
00:22:53,645 --> 00:22:55,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you say it's romantic?</font>

404
00:22:56,345 --> 00:22:57,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Think carefully.</font>

405
00:22:58,745 --> 00:23:02,305
<font color=#FFFF00>You're such a happy woman.</font>

406
00:23:04,005 --> 00:23:07,105
<font color=#FFFF00>There's hardly anyone who can still date a guy in your age.</font>

