612
00:34:08,575 --> 00:34:10,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui, do you have any clue?</font>

613
00:34:12,805 --> 00:34:14,045
<font color=#FFFF00>I think...</font>

614
00:34:14,305 --> 00:34:17,005
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard that he's going to a province.</font>

615
00:34:17,475 --> 00:34:21,345
<font color=#FFFF00>To a province? Which province? Did he go on a business trip?</font>

616
00:34:21,705 --> 00:34:22,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Hong, did he?</font>

617
00:34:23,575 --> 00:34:24,775
<font color=#FFFF00>I wouldn't know.</font>

618
00:34:26,405 --> 00:34:29,205
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, it feels strange.</font>

619
00:34:29,305 --> 00:34:32,275
<font color=#FFFF00>How does Dong Hui know what we don't know?</font>

620
00:34:32,275 --> 00:34:34,275
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - I know.</font>

621
00:34:35,545 --> 00:34:37,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop being so ridiculous.</font>

622
00:34:37,445 --> 00:34:41,045
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't help suspecting them when there are young people.</font>

623
00:34:41,275 --> 00:34:43,745
<font color=#FFFF00>It's just that we're bored. We are bored.</font>

624
00:34:46,775 --> 00:34:48,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han is acting strange these days.</font>

625
00:34:49,205 --> 00:34:51,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Where did he go...</font>

626
00:34:51,305 --> 00:34:54,115
<font color=#FFFF00>at this important time?</font>

627
00:35:11,275 --> 00:35:12,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Where's Mom and Dad?</font>

628
00:35:12,805 --> 00:35:14,805
<font color=#FFFF00>They seemed very weak,</font>

629
00:35:14,875 --> 00:35:16,875
<font color=#FFFF00>so I cooked chicken porridge for them.</font>

630
00:35:18,445 --> 00:35:20,375
<font color=#FFFF00>You should've treated them better before.</font>

631
00:35:20,875 --> 00:35:21,905
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

632
00:35:22,045 --> 00:35:24,505
<font color=#FFFF00>What's the use of cooking them chicken porridge?</font>

633
00:35:24,505 --> 00:35:26,905
<font color=#FFFF00>You all failed and invaded their place.</font>

634
00:35:28,205 --> 00:35:31,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo even brought her family with her.</font>

635
00:35:31,845 --> 00:35:33,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa!</font>

636
00:35:33,705 --> 00:35:36,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa, you should eat.</font>

637
00:35:36,445 --> 00:35:38,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. Give me a glass of water.</font>

638
00:35:39,075 --> 00:35:40,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure.</font>

639
00:35:40,875 --> 00:35:42,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Wait. I'll get you a glass of water.</font>

640
00:35:43,805 --> 00:35:44,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Here you go.</font>

641
00:35:51,145 --> 00:35:52,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it.</font>

642
00:35:54,305 --> 00:35:55,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon. Ah In.</font>

643
00:35:56,045 --> 00:35:57,975
<font color=#FFFF00>- Here are sausages. - Thank you.</font>

644
00:35:58,475 --> 00:36:02,045
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aunt. What about me? - Ask your mother.</font>

645
00:36:03,245 --> 00:36:05,615
<font color=#FFFF00>Here's a delicious salad for you, Chang Soo.</font>

646
00:36:06,945 --> 00:36:10,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom. A salad won't be enough for me to sing.</font>

647
00:36:10,445 --> 00:36:14,345
<font color=#FFFF00>You should still eat it. You didn't have vegetables today.</font>

648
00:36:14,505 --> 00:36:17,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. I will then if you say so.</font>

649
00:36:18,745 --> 00:36:21,775
<font color=#FFFF00>What a nice boy. How can you listen to me so well?</font>

650
00:36:21,775 --> 00:36:24,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Good boy. You are such a good son.</font>

651
00:36:24,645 --> 00:36:27,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom. What a soft touch you have.</font>

652
00:36:29,375 --> 00:36:32,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, you. You are so over the top.</font>

653
00:36:32,145 --> 00:36:33,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it. Hye Joo.</font>

654
00:36:33,975 --> 00:36:35,205
<font color=#FFFF00>It's because I didn't eat sausages.</font>

655
00:36:37,945 --> 00:36:40,575
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you act like this?</font>

656
00:36:41,705 --> 00:36:45,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa. What is your point now?</font>

657
00:36:45,375 --> 00:36:47,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you really want to live having your children switched?</font>

658
00:36:47,975 --> 00:36:50,145
<font color=#FFFF00>What is this mess? It's confusing me since I was away.</font>

659
00:36:50,245 --> 00:36:53,205
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jeong Hwa. What happened was... - Jeong Hwa.</font>

660
00:36:55,375 --> 00:36:57,775
<font color=#FFFF00>This is a settled matter.</font>

661
00:36:58,145 --> 00:37:00,615
<font color=#FFFF00>We had a difficult time coping with the switch.</font>

662
00:37:00,615 --> 00:37:03,405
<font color=#FFFF00>You might be confused since you were away.</font>

663
00:37:03,405 --> 00:37:06,545
<font color=#FFFF00>From our perspective, you are beating a dead horse.</font>

664
00:37:08,745 --> 00:37:09,775
<font color=#FFFF00>So what?</font>

665
00:37:09,945 --> 00:37:13,245
<font color=#FFFF00>So you should just have you meal. Make sure you chew well. Okay?</font>

666
00:37:14,005 --> 00:37:16,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom, I don't want to eat.</font>

667
00:37:16,545 --> 00:37:19,615
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? You have to eat a lot if you want to grow taller.</font>

668
00:37:20,045 --> 00:37:22,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo. Make a fried egg for Ye Bin.</font>

669
00:37:24,145 --> 00:37:26,045
<font color=#FFFF00>A fried egg?</font>

670
00:37:26,575 --> 00:37:28,675
<font color=#FFFF00>- Calm down. - Make one please.</font>

671
00:37:28,905 --> 00:37:31,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure. I will make one right away.</font>

672
00:37:46,175 --> 00:37:49,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo. How did you end up learning vocal music?</font>

673
00:37:49,505 --> 00:37:52,505
<font color=#FFFF00>My school teacher recommended it.</font>

674
00:37:54,145 --> 00:37:55,475
<font color=#FFFF00>You know what?</font>

675
00:37:55,745 --> 00:37:58,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Pavarotti isn't good at singing because he's fat.</font>

676
00:37:58,615 --> 00:38:02,115
<font color=#FFFF00>It's because he's a good opera singer, we don't hold it against it.</font>

677
00:38:03,275 --> 00:38:05,475
<font color=#FFFF00>You should lose some weight.</font>

678
00:38:05,675 --> 00:38:08,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Nowadays, opera singers are slim and handsome.</font>

679
00:38:08,475 --> 00:38:10,675
<font color=#FFFF00>They watch their figure like a soccer player.</font>

680
00:38:12,475 --> 00:38:14,675
<font color=#FFFF00>- Okay. - And you, Ji Hoon.</font>

681
00:38:15,305 --> 00:38:18,575
<font color=#FFFF00>- Are you going to be a magician? - Yes. I plan on it.</font>

682
00:38:19,075 --> 00:38:22,575
<font color=#FFFF00>You think every magician succeeds like David Copperfield.</font>

683
00:38:22,975 --> 00:38:24,115
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not true.</font>

684
00:38:24,475 --> 00:38:27,945
<font color=#FFFF00>You know people make desperate effort in order to become magicians.</font>

685
00:38:27,945 --> 00:38:31,305
<font color=#FFFF00>If you don't put all of your effort into it, you will end up...</font>

686
00:38:31,305 --> 00:38:34,275
<font color=#FFFF00>taking out a rabbit or a pigeon out of a hat at a preschool recital.</font>

687
00:38:34,845 --> 00:38:36,745
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - And you, Ah In.</font>

688
00:38:37,305 --> 00:38:40,175
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes? - Can't you speak English well?</font>

689
00:38:40,345 --> 00:38:42,405
<font color=#FFFF00>"Hi. How are you? I'm fine. Thank you." Is this all you can do?</font>

690
00:38:42,575 --> 00:38:46,075
<font color=#FFFF00>I think for the time we stay here, you should learn from Ye Bin.</font>

691
00:38:46,205 --> 00:38:47,205
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

692
00:38:52,905 --> 00:38:55,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo. Calm down.</font>

693
00:38:56,245 --> 00:38:59,205
<font color=#FFFF00>How can I calm down? She treats us like servants. She says things...</font>

694
00:38:59,205 --> 00:39:01,805
<font color=#FFFF00>she shouldn't say in front of our children. How can I stay calm?</font>

695
00:39:03,005 --> 00:39:05,045
<font color=#FFFF00>She's stressed out.</font>

696
00:39:05,045 --> 00:39:08,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I told her this morning that she's not the only one who's stressed out.</font>

697
00:39:08,805 --> 00:39:11,675
<font color=#FFFF00>What will you do? Will you fight in front of Father rand Mother?</font>

698
00:39:11,745 --> 00:39:14,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me know if a daughter-in-law won after fighting her sister-in-law.</font>

699
00:39:14,205 --> 00:39:15,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Then should I back off?</font>

700
00:39:16,145 --> 00:39:19,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Then are you going to get a sword and lead a troop?</font>

701
00:39:20,645 --> 00:39:21,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Please compose yourself.</font>

702
00:39:22,115 --> 00:39:24,845
<font color=#FFFF00>It doesn't matter. We will forever be subordinates to her.</font>

703
00:39:25,875 --> 00:39:29,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook. Since when have you become obedient...</font>

704
00:39:29,205 --> 00:39:30,845
<font color=#FFFF00>and accommodating?</font>

705
00:39:31,305 --> 00:39:33,075
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't know me well.</font>

706
00:39:33,115 --> 00:39:34,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Except for my children's education,</font>

707
00:39:34,975 --> 00:39:37,675
<font color=#FFFF00>I was always obedient and accommodating.</font>

708
00:39:40,845 --> 00:39:42,045
<font color=#FFFF00>My husband...</font>

709
00:39:42,805 --> 00:39:46,075
<font color=#FFFF00>cheated on me with that Anchor Jang Yoo Ra.</font>

710
00:39:46,245 --> 00:39:49,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Even though the whole country knows about the affair,</font>

711
00:39:49,675 --> 00:39:51,745
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't even bat an eye.</font>

712
00:39:52,145 --> 00:39:54,805
<font color=#FFFF00>It only took me four days to recover.</font>

713
00:39:55,505 --> 00:39:58,175
<font color=#FFFF00>In that sense, I hold you to the highest respect.</font>

714
00:39:58,545 --> 00:40:02,615
<font color=#FFFF00>Some people are never meant to grow up. It's water under the bridge.</font>

715
00:40:03,205 --> 00:40:05,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa is one of them.</font>

716
00:40:06,045 --> 00:40:08,175
<font color=#FFFF00>She will never come to her senses.</font>

717
00:40:08,575 --> 00:40:10,975
<font color=#FFFF00>So let's not turn this into a big deal.</font>

718
00:40:10,975 --> 00:40:13,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Why don't we just hold back? Okay, Hye Joo?</font>

719
00:40:13,345 --> 00:40:15,145
<font color=#FFFF00>- But still... - Hye Joo.</font>

720
00:40:15,275 --> 00:40:16,775
<font color=#FFFF00>All right. You're so close we might kiss.</font>

721
00:40:16,775 --> 00:40:19,575
<font color=#FFFF00>- So what? - Have you gone mad?</font>

722
00:40:20,705 --> 00:40:22,505
<font color=#FFFF00>- Calm down. - Stop it.</font>

723
00:40:25,045 --> 00:40:27,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa. Where are the children?</font>

724
00:40:28,345 --> 00:40:31,775
<font color=#FFFF00>- They went down after we talked. - They did?</font>

725
00:40:32,645 --> 00:40:35,875
<font color=#FFFF00>I see. Are you going somewhere at this late hour?</font>

726
00:40:35,905 --> 00:40:37,875
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to buy coffee. We ran out. Why?</font>

727
00:40:37,875 --> 00:40:40,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you going to get it for me? I need to help Ye Bin brush her teeth.</font>

728
00:40:40,505 --> 00:40:44,645
<font color=#FFFF00>What a shame. I have to help Ah In brush her teeth too.</font>

729
00:40:46,345 --> 00:40:48,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you ask if you weren't going to get it for me?</font>

730
00:40:49,305 --> 00:40:51,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. Are you all right, Jeong Hwa?</font>

731
00:40:56,115 --> 00:40:58,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa. Are you okay?</font>

732
00:40:58,305 --> 00:41:01,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you hurt? You should've been more careful.</font>

733
00:41:01,705 --> 00:41:04,845
<font color=#FFFF00>You should stop by a pharmacy too.</font>

734
00:41:07,405 --> 00:41:09,005
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hye Joo. - What?</font>

735
00:41:15,445 --> 00:41:17,615
<font color=#FFFF00>- What are you doing? - You're here.</font>

736
00:41:18,145 --> 00:41:19,645
<font color=#FFFF00>What is that?</font>

737
00:41:19,775 --> 00:41:21,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Is this yours?</font>

738
00:41:23,405 --> 00:41:25,445
<font color=#FFFF00>No, it's not. Where did you get it?</font>

739
00:41:27,075 --> 00:41:29,905
<font color=#FFFF00>- This is weird. - What is weird?</font>

740
00:41:30,645 --> 00:41:31,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Never mind.</font>

741
00:41:32,775 --> 00:41:34,245
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, you don't look so good.</font>

742
00:41:35,575 --> 00:41:38,375
<font color=#FFFF00>- It's because of Seong Joon. - What is it?</font>

743
00:41:38,615 --> 00:41:40,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Did something happen to him?</font>

744
00:41:40,575 --> 00:41:43,145
<font color=#FFFF00>He hasn't come home for days without calling us.</font>

745
00:41:43,505 --> 00:41:44,845
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought he was on a business trip.</font>

746
00:41:45,045 --> 00:41:47,805
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what Dong Hui said.</font>

747
00:41:48,405 --> 00:41:50,805
<font color=#FFFF00>It doesn't matter how urgent it is.</font>

748
00:41:50,975 --> 00:41:54,945
<font color=#FFFF00>He never forgets to call and inform us.</font>

749
00:41:55,145 --> 00:41:56,875
<font color=#FFFF00>That's right.</font>

750
00:41:58,345 --> 00:41:59,645
<font color=#FFFF00>I think...</font>

751
00:42:00,745 --> 00:42:03,745
<font color=#FFFF00>- it's because of Jeong Hwa. - What?</font>

752
00:42:04,075 --> 00:42:06,875
<font color=#FFFF00>You know how Jeong Hwa bullies him.</font>

753
00:42:06,875 --> 00:42:08,675
<font color=#FFFF00>She even bullied him on the day he came here.</font>

754
00:42:08,745 --> 00:42:11,775
<font color=#FFFF00>He thinks he's not welcomed even if we welcome him.</font>

755
00:42:12,205 --> 00:42:15,045
<font color=#FFFF00>It must've been hard on him. He must have felt uncomfortable...</font>

756
00:42:15,245 --> 00:42:19,345
<font color=#FFFF00>after finding out Jeong Hwa will stay with us for a while.</font>

757
00:42:19,975 --> 00:42:22,475
<font color=#FFFF00>You know that Jeong Hwa isn't exactly the agreeable type.</font>

758
00:42:23,905 --> 00:42:26,115
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, you need to reflect on your wrongdoings.</font>

759
00:42:26,445 --> 00:42:28,845
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you not to spoil her.</font>

760
00:42:29,205 --> 00:42:31,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Just because she was your only daughter,</font>

761
00:42:31,615 --> 00:42:35,045
<font color=#FFFF00>you spoiled her by treating her like a princess.</font>

762
00:42:35,275 --> 00:42:38,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Look how selfish she turned out to be.</font>

763
00:42:39,745 --> 00:42:42,045
<font color=#FFFF00>I have no one to blame, but myself.</font>

764
00:42:45,045 --> 00:42:47,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh. Poor Seong Joon.</font>

765
00:42:56,075 --> 00:42:58,145
<font color=#FFFF00>(A car accident in Bangbae-dong, 1993)</font>

766
00:43:03,045 --> 00:43:04,045
<font color=#FFFF00>(Geumbit Academy's bus was turned over.)</font>

767
00:43:08,145 --> 00:43:11,745
<font color=#FFFF00>(Geumbit Academy's bus)</font>

768
00:43:26,675 --> 00:43:30,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyung Seop drove your father to death.</font>

769
00:43:47,845 --> 00:43:51,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Think of Dong Hui as your cousin and get along with her.</font>

770
00:43:51,945 --> 00:43:53,445
<font color=#FFFF00>If she were alive,</font>

771
00:43:54,205 --> 00:43:56,845
<font color=#FFFF00>she'd be the biggest shareholder. Do you know that?</font>

772
00:43:57,345 --> 00:43:58,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Then you will have no place in this company.</font>

773
00:43:59,545 --> 00:44:02,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Is Ms. Oh that important to you, Dad?</font>

774
00:44:02,575 --> 00:44:05,575
<font color=#FFFF00>20 years ago, she was a very special person...</font>

775
00:44:06,445 --> 00:44:08,245
<font color=#FFFF00>for your grandmother.</font>

776
00:44:16,245 --> 00:44:19,745
<font color=#FFFF00>This is Bang Mi Joo. Under Oh Dong Hui's family history,</font>

777
00:44:19,805 --> 00:44:21,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Gui Boon should be listed.</font>

778
00:44:22,005 --> 00:44:23,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you do a background check on her?</font>

779
00:44:25,275 --> 00:44:28,605
<font color=#FFFF00>And get me the files regarding Chairwoman Park's disappearance.</font>

780
00:44:31,175 --> 00:44:33,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you feeling better?</font>

781
00:44:34,105 --> 00:44:36,345
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I am.</font>

782
00:44:36,605 --> 00:44:38,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Perhaps, you were exhausted.</font>

783
00:44:40,105 --> 00:44:41,305
<font color=#FFFF00>No, I wasn't.</font>

784
00:44:42,505 --> 00:44:44,045
<font color=#FFFF00>My house is quite big.</font>

785
00:44:45,545 --> 00:44:47,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, people with resources...</font>

786
00:44:49,045 --> 00:44:51,745
<font color=#FFFF00>always live in a big house.</font>

787
00:44:52,205 --> 00:44:55,945
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, I think my father relies on you a lot.</font>

788
00:44:57,345 --> 00:44:59,075
<font color=#FFFF00>He doesn't rely on me.</font>

789
00:44:59,245 --> 00:45:01,705
<font color=#FFFF00>It's just because I raised him since he was young.</font>

790
00:45:01,975 --> 00:45:03,745
<font color=#FFFF00>It's just an attachment, nothing else.</font>

791
00:45:04,345 --> 00:45:07,405
<font color=#FFFF00>From what I have gathered, I learned you were quite close...</font>

792
00:45:07,605 --> 00:45:09,105
<font color=#FFFF00>with my grandmother who passed away.</font>

793
00:45:12,845 --> 00:45:15,645
<font color=#FFFF00>She did take good care of me.</font>

794
00:45:16,845 --> 00:45:19,405
<font color=#FFFF00>It was after I lost my husband.</font>

795
00:45:19,975 --> 00:45:23,145
<font color=#FFFF00>I relied on her quite a lot.</font>

796
00:45:24,475 --> 00:45:28,045
<font color=#FFFF00>She understood and looked out for me.</font>

797
00:45:29,075 --> 00:45:32,605
<font color=#FFFF00>My gratitude towards her still hasn't changed.</font>

798
00:45:33,875 --> 00:45:37,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Then you must be aware of...</font>

799
00:45:37,645 --> 00:45:38,975
<font color=#FFFF00>my grandmother's disappearance.</font>

800
00:45:40,205 --> 00:45:42,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I was informed after her disappearance.</font>

801
00:45:44,145 --> 00:45:47,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Actually, I came to ask you something.</font>

802
00:45:49,545 --> 00:45:53,005
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think the reason why my dad is putting off reporting...</font>

803
00:45:53,105 --> 00:45:55,475
<font color=#FFFF00>my grandmother's death is because he believes she is still alive.</font>

804
00:45:56,005 --> 00:45:59,145
<font color=#FFFF00>If it is, he shouldn't have reported Hyun Jeong's death either.</font>

805
00:46:02,505 --> 00:46:04,405
<font color=#FFFF00>If he admits that my grandmother is dead,</font>

806
00:46:04,875 --> 00:46:06,975
<font color=#FFFF00>her will would automatically be revealed.</font>

807
00:46:08,075 --> 00:46:11,775
<font color=#FFFF00>He must be afraid of what the will might state.</font>

808
00:46:12,975 --> 00:46:14,045
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I wanted to ask you...</font>

809
00:46:15,445 --> 00:46:17,875
<font color=#FFFF00>if you know what my grandmother's will says.</font>

810
00:46:20,105 --> 00:46:22,675
<font color=#FFFF00>How can I know what it says?</font>

811
00:46:22,675 --> 00:46:25,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you have a copy of it then?</font>

812
00:46:26,345 --> 00:46:29,045
<font color=#FFFF00>No. That's not possible.</font>

813
00:46:29,045 --> 00:46:32,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Does it say anything about Bang Hyun Jeong,</font>

814
00:46:32,445 --> 00:46:33,745
<font color=#FFFF00>my cousin?</font>

815
00:46:34,545 --> 00:46:37,145
<font color=#FFFF00>No. I don't know that.</font>

816
00:46:38,045 --> 00:46:39,105
<font color=#FFFF00>Really?</font>

817
00:46:40,175 --> 00:46:41,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course.</font>

818
00:46:41,705 --> 00:46:44,175
<font color=#FFFF00>How would I know anything about it?</font>

819
00:46:44,575 --> 00:46:47,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Even your father doesn't know what it says.</font>

820
00:46:49,045 --> 00:46:52,075
<font color=#FFFF00>There is no way a mere housekeeper like me knows what it's about.</font>

821
00:46:55,745 --> 00:46:58,175
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think my grandmother's alive.</font>

822
00:46:58,505 --> 00:47:00,905
<font color=#FFFF00>It's been 20 years since her disappearance.</font>

823
00:47:01,505 --> 00:47:02,905
<font color=#FFFF00>I believe...</font>

824
00:47:03,375 --> 00:47:05,775
<font color=#FFFF00>we should follow her will whether it's advantageous...</font>

825
00:47:06,745 --> 00:47:09,375
<font color=#FFFF00>to me and my dad or not. It's what she wanted.</font>

826
00:47:10,405 --> 00:47:11,705
<font color=#FFFF00>I want you...</font>

827
00:47:11,945 --> 00:47:14,145
<font color=#FFFF00>to convince my dad to report my grandmother's death...</font>

828
00:47:14,675 --> 00:47:16,345
<font color=#FFFF00>as soon as possible.</font>

829
00:47:16,845 --> 00:47:19,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I know my dad relies on you like you're his real mother.</font>

830
00:47:20,275 --> 00:47:22,175
<font color=#FFFF00>You can at least do that, right?</font>

831
00:47:25,275 --> 00:47:26,375
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not sure.</font>

832
00:47:27,375 --> 00:47:29,005
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know if I can.</font>

833
00:47:32,745 --> 00:47:33,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Besides,</font>

834
00:47:37,345 --> 00:47:38,645
<font color=#FFFF00>wouldn't it be possible...</font>

835
00:47:39,475 --> 00:47:40,505
<font color=#FFFF00>that your grandmother...</font>

836
00:47:41,275 --> 00:47:43,775
<font color=#FFFF00>is still alive somewhere?</font>

837
00:47:44,175 --> 00:47:45,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Pardon?</font>

838
00:47:45,405 --> 00:47:49,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Your grandmother is such a strong person.</font>

839
00:47:49,575 --> 00:47:51,275
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you talking about?</font>

840
00:47:54,445 --> 00:47:55,645
<font color=#FFFF00>It's nothing.</font>

841
00:47:57,805 --> 00:48:01,575
<font color=#FFFF00>I suddenly started to miss her.</font>

842
00:48:02,975 --> 00:48:06,905
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm greatly indebted to her.</font>

843
00:48:19,845 --> 00:48:21,505
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing here?</font>

844
00:48:22,005 --> 00:48:24,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? Can't I be here?</font>

845
00:48:24,475 --> 00:48:26,275
<font color=#FFFF00>You came to my place the other day,</font>

846
00:48:26,375 --> 00:48:27,975
<font color=#FFFF00>so I came to yours this time.</font>

847
00:48:28,075 --> 00:48:29,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I'm being childish?</font>

848
00:48:30,145 --> 00:48:32,105
<font color=#FFFF00>No. I'm glad you came.</font>

849
00:48:32,275 --> 00:48:35,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Please come back inside. I'll cook you some noodles.</font>

850
00:48:35,345 --> 00:48:36,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is Director Han?</font>

851
00:48:37,005 --> 00:48:38,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Has he come back yet?</font>

852
00:48:39,775 --> 00:48:40,805
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

853
00:48:40,805 --> 00:48:42,445
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you think the reason is?</font>

854
00:48:43,175 --> 00:48:44,775
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not sure.</font>

855
00:48:44,845 --> 00:48:48,145
<font color=#FFFF00>He has never behaved this way for the last five years.</font>

856
00:48:48,205 --> 00:48:50,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you saying I'm responsible for this as well?</font>

857
00:48:50,505 --> 00:48:53,775
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm just saying you're good at meddling in others' business.</font>

858
00:48:55,045 --> 00:48:57,075
<font color=#FFFF00>If your scripts for episodes 3 and 4 don't get picked,</font>

859
00:48:57,075 --> 00:48:58,845
<font color=#FFFF00>you should give up completely. You know that, right?</font>

860
00:48:58,875 --> 00:49:00,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. I do know that.</font>

861
00:49:00,875 --> 00:49:03,175
<font color=#FFFF00>- Quit your job at the company too. - Excuse me?</font>

862
00:49:03,545 --> 00:49:05,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to be involved with you anymore.</font>

863
00:49:06,245 --> 00:49:07,945
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll pay off your brother's debt...</font>

864
00:49:07,975 --> 00:49:09,675
<font color=#FFFF00>with my own money.</font>

865
00:49:10,005 --> 00:49:13,205
<font color=#FFFF00>If your scripts don't get picked, please resign.</font>

866
00:49:14,075 --> 00:49:17,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Also, stop coming to my house even if my dad asks you to.</font>

867
00:49:17,845 --> 00:49:20,575
<font color=#FFFF00>We see each other at work and at home too.</font>

868
00:49:20,705 --> 00:49:22,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Isn't that too tiring for both of us?</font>

869
00:49:22,645 --> 00:49:25,645
<font color=#FFFF00>You're the one who came to my house today.</font>

870
00:49:25,705 --> 00:49:28,305
<font color=#FFFF00>This isn't your house. It's Director Han's house.</font>

871
00:49:29,145 --> 00:49:31,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Please tell him to call me when he comes back.</font>

872
00:49:40,045 --> 00:49:41,875
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to become a famous writer,</font>

873
00:49:42,105 --> 00:49:44,575
<font color=#FFFF00>and I'm never going to work with you.</font>

874
00:49:44,905 --> 00:49:46,375
<font color=#FFFF00>You will see.</font>

875
00:49:50,775 --> 00:49:53,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Stay still. I'm going to dry your hair for you.</font>

876
00:49:54,445 --> 00:49:55,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother. I'm here.</font>

877
00:49:56,345 --> 00:49:59,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you come? You should be making dinner downstairs.</font>

878
00:49:59,175 --> 00:50:02,145
<font color=#FFFF00>No. I didn't want you to take care of Ye Bin by yourself.</font>

879
00:50:02,205 --> 00:50:03,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is Father?</font>

880
00:50:03,445 --> 00:50:06,475
<font color=#FFFF00>He went to the supermarket to buy yogurt for Ye Bin.</font>

881
00:50:06,645 --> 00:50:09,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Please give me that towel. I'll dry her hair.</font>

882
00:50:10,045 --> 00:50:11,075
<font color=#FFFF00>All right.</font>

883
00:50:11,245 --> 00:50:14,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Ye Bin. Let's sit on the sofa. I'll dry your hair.</font>

884
00:50:22,675 --> 00:50:24,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother. I know you must be upset.</font>

885
00:50:26,575 --> 00:50:27,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course, I am.</font>

886
00:50:28,345 --> 00:50:29,675
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure there will be a solution.</font>

887
00:50:30,005 --> 00:50:33,145
<font color=#FFFF00>No, there isn't. They've already filed a suit.</font>

888
00:50:33,145 --> 00:50:34,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing will solve it now.</font>

889
00:50:36,275 --> 00:50:38,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa and her husband didn't understand each other.</font>

890
00:50:38,975 --> 00:50:41,075
<font color=#FFFF00>It'll be better for Jeong Hwa to just split up with him.</font>

891
00:50:42,105 --> 00:50:43,275
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not sure...</font>

892
00:50:43,805 --> 00:50:45,305
<font color=#FFFF00>if she's doing the right thing.</font>

893
00:50:46,375 --> 00:50:48,645
<font color=#FFFF00>You still shouldn't stay inside the house all day.</font>

894
00:50:48,645 --> 00:50:50,075
<font color=#FFFF00>It'll stress you out more.</font>

895
00:50:50,545 --> 00:50:52,345
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you have aerobics classes anymore?</font>

896
00:50:53,375 --> 00:50:56,375
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't have time to go to aerobics classes.</font>

897
00:50:57,245 --> 00:51:00,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa is causing trouble now right after Seong Sik's scandal.</font>

898
00:51:00,905 --> 00:51:04,045
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm too embarrassed to even go out of the house now.</font>

899
00:51:04,445 --> 00:51:08,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Besides, I have to babysit Ye Bin. I can't go anywhere.</font>

900
00:51:09,305 --> 00:51:11,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is Jeong Hwa?</font>

901
00:51:11,405 --> 00:51:13,875
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know. She just went out.</font>

902
00:51:14,545 --> 00:51:15,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Where did she go?</font>

903
00:51:23,475 --> 00:51:26,275
<font color=#FFFF00>You're as beautiful as always, Ms. Han.</font>

904
00:51:27,405 --> 00:51:30,175
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not true. I'm a woman who has a child now.</font>

905
00:51:30,345 --> 00:51:33,245
<font color=#FFFF00>It's true. You don't look much different from before.</font>

906
00:51:33,545 --> 00:51:35,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you, sir.</font>

907
00:51:35,375 --> 00:51:37,705
<font color=#FFFF00>All right. Are you back for good?</font>

908
00:51:37,875 --> 00:51:39,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. I guess so.</font>

909
00:51:39,975 --> 00:51:42,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you want to meet me because you wanted to come back to work?</font>

910
00:51:43,005 --> 00:51:46,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. If you give me a good show to host, I won't say no.</font>

911
00:51:47,745 --> 00:51:51,345
<font color=#FFFF00>But you'll have to compete with the young anchors.</font>

912
00:51:53,205 --> 00:51:55,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. I suppose.</font>

913
00:51:56,205 --> 00:51:58,675
<font color=#FFFF00>It's very hard to host a good show...</font>

914
00:51:59,275 --> 00:52:02,705
<font color=#FFFF00>even for young and popular anchors.</font>

915
00:52:04,845 --> 00:52:06,005
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

916
00:52:08,675 --> 00:52:10,475
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing this weekend?</font>

917
00:52:10,705 --> 00:52:12,905
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sorry? - Do you want to play golf with me?</font>

918
00:52:16,205 --> 00:52:17,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure.</font>

919
00:52:26,575 --> 00:52:27,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

920
00:52:32,775 --> 00:52:33,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa.</font>

921
00:52:37,905 --> 00:52:38,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

922
00:52:54,405 --> 00:52:56,545
<font color=#FFFF00>You look tired today.</font>

923
00:52:57,075 --> 00:52:58,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Am I wrong?</font>

924
00:52:59,445 --> 00:53:02,475
<font color=#FFFF00>You're right. I had a long day.</font>

925
00:53:04,245 --> 00:53:05,345
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you have any beer?</font>

926
00:53:05,645 --> 00:53:07,605
<font color=#FFFF00>I think beer suits this house...</font>

927
00:53:07,605 --> 00:53:09,645
<font color=#FFFF00>better than coffee.</font>

928
00:53:10,905 --> 00:53:11,945
<font color=#FFFF00>I got both.</font>

929
00:53:25,945 --> 00:53:27,605
<font color=#FFFF00>You keep your place very neat.</font>

930
00:53:27,775 --> 00:53:29,845
<font color=#FFFF00>It feels as if you're only staying here temporarily.</font>

931
00:53:32,845 --> 00:53:33,975
<font color=#FFFF00>It's just my personality.</font>

932
00:53:42,245 --> 00:53:44,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Beer tastes great when I feel frustrated.</font>

933
00:53:46,975 --> 00:53:49,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you worried about something?</font>

934
00:53:51,145 --> 00:53:53,175
<font color=#FFFF00>No one has given me a job yet.</font>

935
00:53:53,705 --> 00:53:56,975
<font color=#FFFF00>I knew it would be hard to go back to work after seven years,</font>

936
00:53:57,445 --> 00:53:59,875
<font color=#FFFF00>but I'm a little upset because it's not going so well.</font>

937
00:54:03,575 --> 00:54:04,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

938
00:54:05,105 --> 00:54:06,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Would you like me to help you?</font>

939
00:54:08,575 --> 00:54:11,005
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm still confused whether you're just being kind...</font>

940
00:54:12,545 --> 00:54:13,745
<font color=#FFFF00>or you're interested in me.</font>

941
00:54:21,045 --> 00:54:22,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it ugly?</font>

942
00:54:24,605 --> 00:54:26,275
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a deep scar.</font>

943
00:54:27,905 --> 00:54:29,405
<font color=#FFFF00>I had a big accident.</font>

944
00:54:30,845 --> 00:54:31,905
<font color=#FFFF00>An accident?</font>

945
00:54:33,205 --> 00:54:36,305
<font color=#FFFF00>That accident left a scar on my life.</font>

946
00:54:36,575 --> 00:54:38,375
<font color=#FFFF00>A scar that can't be forever removed.</font>

947
00:55:01,705 --> 00:55:02,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Did it hurt?</font>

948
00:55:04,105 --> 00:55:05,245
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not sure.</font>

949
00:55:05,945 --> 00:55:07,405
<font color=#FFFF00>It must have hurt a lot.</font>

950
00:55:12,105 --> 00:55:13,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Why?</font>

951
00:55:17,075 --> 00:55:18,175
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a scar that...</font>

952
00:55:18,745 --> 00:55:20,445
<font color=#FFFF00>doesn't suit such a beauty like you.</font>

953
00:55:27,905 --> 00:55:29,345
<font color=#FFFF00>Shall we go and get some fresh air?</font>

954
00:55:40,005 --> 00:55:42,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, my. You can see our house so well from here.</font>

955
00:55:46,105 --> 00:55:47,775
<font color=#FFFF00>You can see the whole neighborhood here.</font>

956
00:55:49,345 --> 00:55:53,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Our house looks so old now. It used to be the best building before.</font>

957
00:55:55,075 --> 00:55:56,375
<font color=#FFFF00>It should be rebuilt.</font>

958
00:56:00,245 --> 00:56:01,875
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you think about Channel T?</font>

959
00:56:02,005 --> 00:56:04,675
<font color=#FFFF00>I think you'll be great on a show about current events.</font>

960
00:56:05,505 --> 00:56:06,905
<font color=#FFFF00>You're a competent man.</font>

961
00:56:07,345 --> 00:56:09,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Well... I thought you knew.</font>

962
00:56:10,445 --> 00:56:13,005
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you want me to do in return?</font>

963
00:56:25,345 --> 00:56:27,745
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not sure. Why don't you...</font>

964
00:56:28,205 --> 00:56:30,045
<font color=#FFFF00>give me some time to think about it?</font>

965
00:56:31,845 --> 00:56:33,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you always like this?</font>

966
00:56:35,005 --> 00:56:37,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Well... On some level.</font>

967
00:56:51,145 --> 00:56:53,245
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a bit cold. Shall we go back in?</font>

968
00:56:53,375 --> 00:56:56,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. I think we got enough fresh air.</font>

969
00:57:04,745 --> 00:57:05,975
<font color=#FFFF00>I just don't know...</font>

970
00:57:07,045 --> 00:57:10,105
<font color=#FFFF00>what you're trying to get from doing this.</font>

971
00:57:19,445 --> 00:57:21,445
<font color=#FFFF00>I actually felt very lonely today.</font>

972
00:57:22,445 --> 00:57:23,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

973
00:57:25,175 --> 00:57:28,205
<font color=#FFFF00>I also felt lonely today. Thank you for a lovely time.</font>

974
00:57:31,575 --> 00:57:32,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you still single?</font>

975
00:57:34,345 --> 00:57:35,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you getting divorced?</font>

976
00:57:39,075 --> 00:57:40,105
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

977
00:57:41,745 --> 00:57:44,405
<font color=#FFFF00>If I had known such a great man was living across from my house,</font>

978
00:57:44,545 --> 00:57:46,375
<font color=#FFFF00>I would've come back sooner.</font>

979
00:57:48,245 --> 00:57:49,805
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel the same way.</font>

980
00:57:52,605 --> 00:57:53,745
<font color=#FFFF00>I can go by myself from here.</font>

981
00:57:57,005 --> 00:57:59,905
<font color=#FFFF00>- I guess that's better. - Good night.</font>

982
00:58:00,905 --> 00:58:02,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Good night, Jeong Hwa.</font>

983
00:58:20,505 --> 00:58:21,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Please don't do this.</font>

984
00:58:23,145 --> 00:58:24,705
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel like dying.</font>

985
00:58:25,545 --> 00:58:27,445
<font color=#FFFF00>I really feel like I'm going to die.</font>

986
00:58:31,445 --> 00:58:33,145
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jeong Eun. - That's right.</font>

987
00:58:33,445 --> 00:58:35,775
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm Han Jeong Eun, the woman you once liked.</font>

988
00:58:38,705 --> 00:58:39,945
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you not to come here.</font>

989
00:58:40,275 --> 00:58:44,345
<font color=#FFFF00>How can I not? I can't just let you ruin yourself.</font>

990
00:58:44,845 --> 00:58:46,975
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't let my family get ruined.</font>

991
00:58:47,075 --> 00:58:49,345
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't let myself get ruined.</font>

992
00:58:49,975 --> 00:58:51,445
<font color=#FFFF00>Go and tell them then.</font>

993
00:58:52,975 --> 00:58:55,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Go to your uncle and tell him who I am.</font>

994
00:58:58,105 --> 00:59:00,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo. Please.</font>

995
00:59:01,445 --> 00:59:03,305
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm tired of all this too.</font>

996
00:59:04,205 --> 00:59:06,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell your whole family to settle things with me...</font>

997
00:59:07,475 --> 00:59:08,945
<font color=#FFFF00>once and for all.</font>

998
00:59:47,645 --> 00:59:49,205
<font color=#FFFF00>That's Mr. Lee.</font>

999
00:59:51,745 --> 00:59:53,745
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought he was a decent guy.</font>

1000
00:59:54,045 --> 00:59:55,905
<font color=#FFFF00>What is he doing with a woman on the street?</font>

1001
01:00:00,505 --> 01:00:01,645
<font color=#FFFF00>This is hard for me too.</font>

1002
01:00:03,075 --> 01:00:05,945
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hyun Woo. - Please go back.</font>

1003
01:00:10,645 --> 01:00:13,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo. Hyun Woo!</font>

1004
01:00:37,075 --> 01:00:38,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han.</font>

1005
01:00:42,005 --> 01:00:44,305
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry I made you wait for so long.</font>

1006
01:00:45,905 --> 01:00:47,375
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry I didn't answer my phone.</font>

1007
01:00:48,375 --> 01:00:49,775
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

1008
01:00:52,005 --> 01:00:55,305
<font color=#FFFF00>You look terrible. What happened?</font>

1009
01:00:58,775 --> 01:01:00,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han.</font>

1010
01:01:25,905 --> 01:01:28,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Give me a minute. I'm going to make some tea.</font>

1011
01:01:28,805 --> 01:01:30,305
<font color=#FFFF00>You must be cold. Please sit.</font>

1012
01:01:32,645 --> 01:01:34,105
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

1013
01:01:40,375 --> 01:01:43,075
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong? Why are you doing this?</font>

1014
01:02:43,275 --> 01:02:47,105
<font color=#FFFF00>Why didn't you tell me you were going on a business trip?</font>

1015
01:02:48,505 --> 01:02:51,475
<font color=#FFFF00>What have you been doing? You look haggard.</font>

1016
01:02:51,745 --> 01:02:53,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom. I want my breakfast.</font>

1017
01:02:53,805 --> 01:02:56,005
<font color=#FFFF00>I set it up for you too. Where is Ye Bin?</font>

1018
01:02:56,045 --> 01:02:57,805
<font color=#FFFF00>She's still sleeping. She won't wake up.</font>

1019
01:02:58,545 --> 01:03:00,805
<font color=#FFFF00>- It's been a long time. - Yes.</font>

1020
01:03:01,745 --> 01:03:05,275
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, you can't just go on a business trip without saying a word.</font>

1021
01:03:05,605 --> 01:03:07,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom and Dad were worried about you.</font>

1022
01:03:09,145 --> 01:03:12,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom. Are you the one who raised him so poorly like this?</font>

1023
01:03:12,745 --> 01:03:14,875
<font color=#FFFF00>You're in no place to say such a thing.</font>

1024
01:03:14,875 --> 01:03:17,175
<font color=#FFFF00>You're so immature. You need to grow up.</font>

1025
01:03:17,475 --> 01:03:19,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Still, he shouldn't have done that.</font>

1026
01:03:20,345 --> 01:03:22,105
<font color=#FFFF00>How can he treat his parents so rudely?</font>

1027
01:03:27,805 --> 01:03:29,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you having breakfast, Seong Joon?</font>

1028
01:03:35,575 --> 01:03:36,605
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

1029
01:03:40,045 --> 01:03:41,175
<font color=#FFFF00>What's the matter?</font>

1030
01:03:43,945 --> 01:03:45,075
<font color=#FFFF00>It's nothing.</font>

1031
01:03:46,705 --> 01:03:48,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Is something wrong?</font>

1032
01:03:48,605 --> 01:03:51,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh. Nothing is wrong.</font>

1033
01:03:51,345 --> 01:03:55,105
<font color=#FFFF00>Why is everyone picking on him? Seong Joon. Come on and eat.</font>

1034
01:03:56,845 --> 01:03:58,245
<font color=#FFFF00>You should be quiet too.</font>

1035
01:03:59,345 --> 01:04:01,805
<font color=#FFFF00>You always say mean things at breakfast.</font>

1036
01:04:02,105 --> 01:04:04,475
<font color=#FFFF00>You haven't changed at all.</font>

1037
01:04:05,345 --> 01:04:08,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Well... I'll have breakfast later.</font>

1038
01:04:08,605 --> 01:04:09,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Why?</font>

1039
01:04:12,105 --> 01:04:13,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Excuse me.</font>

1040
01:04:16,445 --> 01:04:18,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, dear. What's wrong with him?</font>

1041
01:04:20,245 --> 01:04:24,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Did he just do that to make me feel uncomfortable? My gosh.</font>

1042
01:04:48,445 --> 01:04:49,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

1043
01:04:54,345 --> 01:04:55,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on out.</font>

1044
01:05:16,405 --> 01:05:17,675
<font color=#FFFF00>What's the matter with you?</font>

1045
01:05:24,445 --> 01:05:26,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you have something to say to me?</font>

1046
01:05:30,245 --> 01:05:31,645
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with you?</font>

1047
01:05:32,945 --> 01:05:34,605
<font color=#FFFF00>You're making me upset.</font>

1048
01:05:37,445 --> 01:05:38,445
<font color=#FFFF00>I have...</font>

1049
01:05:40,645 --> 01:05:42,205
<font color=#FFFF00>something I want to ask you.</font>

1050
01:05:43,505 --> 01:05:44,545
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

1051
01:05:49,605 --> 01:05:50,845
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it?</font>

1052
01:05:53,145 --> 01:05:54,145
<font color=#FFFF00>By any chance,</font>

1053
01:05:57,205 --> 01:05:58,245
<font color=#FFFF00>did you...</font>

1054
01:06:01,105 --> 01:06:03,805
<font color=#FFFF00>make my biological father die?</font>

1055
01:06:08,845 --> 01:06:09,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it true...</font>

1056
01:06:12,675 --> 01:06:15,145
<font color=#FFFF00>that you made my biological father die?</font>

1057
01:06:23,945 --> 01:06:24,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

1058
01:06:49,275 --> 01:06:51,045
<font color=#FFFF00>(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

1059
01:06:51,305 --> 01:06:53,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Checking her identity...</font>

1060
01:06:53,545 --> 01:06:56,645
<font color=#FFFF00>might make us lucky.</font>

1061
01:06:56,705 --> 01:06:57,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Until when...</font>

1062
01:06:58,145 --> 01:07:01,105
<font color=#FFFF00>do I have to live as if I don't exist?</font>

1063
01:07:01,475 --> 01:07:04,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom, Seong Joon has a woman.</font>

1064
01:07:04,345 --> 01:07:06,175
<font color=#FFFF00>It's Dong Hui.</font>

1065
01:07:06,375 --> 01:07:08,575
<font color=#FFFF00>My uncle really believed...</font>

1066
01:07:08,745 --> 01:07:11,145
<font color=#FFFF00>that your father had been drunk-driving.</font>

1067
01:07:11,375 --> 01:07:12,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell me.</font>

1068
01:07:13,005 --> 01:07:16,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Who am I? What are you keeping from me?</font>

